and cultural destination.\n\nThe radiating jewel box emits energy and excitement to the surrounding neighborhood and becomes an inviting new gateway on the skyline, visible from across the water and connecting the Manhattan and Brooklyn waterfronts."},"team":[{"name":"Ellisrael Daing","slug":"ellisrael-daing","primaryOffice":"No Longer Employed","id":"cfd12123-7e06-51d9-9679-e4a3de8c5100"},{"name":"Esteban Varas","slug":"esteban-varas","primaryOffice":"New York","id":"88689f69-2c82-543f-8248-de5e9ed152a8"},{"name":"Oren Manor","slug":"oren-manor","primaryOffice":"No Longer Employed","id":"0b41cff0-f584-5b79-8ca0-d9584157ae5a"},{"name":"Say Lyu","slug":"say-lyu","primaryOffice":"No Longer Employed","id":"7cb5a56d-5df9-5156-8ad4-9c898880bef4"}],"press":null,"photoCredit":["C. Taylor Crothers"],"projectLeader":[{"name":"Carlos Garcia","slug":"carlos-garcia","primaryOffice":"New York","id":"54900713-93a6-5e01-9a98-3c32204d99f7"}],"metadata":{"tags":[]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"the-rooftop-at-pier-17"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1395536887","143701507"],"slicesMap":{}}